entry.string: Select Count(*) as Cantidad, sum(c.importe) as SubTotal, sum(c.importe) * 0.18 as IGV, sum(c.importe) + (sum(c.importe) * 0.18) as ImporteTotal from comprobante c where fecha between '2023-05-01' and '2023-06-03';

SELECT c.apellido AS Apellidos, c.nombre AS Nombre, c.dni AS Dni, co.nro_comp AS Nro_Comprobante, co.fecha AS Fecha, co.importe AS SubTotal, co.importe * 0.18 AS IGV, co.importe + (co.importe * 0.18) AS Importe FROM comprobante co JOIN cliente c ON co.codcli = c.codcli WHERE c.dni = 40567564;

SELECT c.apellido AS Apellidos, c.nombre AS Nombre, c.dni AS Dni, co.nro_comp AS Nro_Comprobante, co.fecha AS Fecha, co.importe AS SubTotal, co.importe * 0.18 AS IGV, co.importe + (co.importe * 0.18) AS Importe FROM comprobante co JOIN cliente c ON co.codcli = c.codcli WHERE c.apellido = 'MENDOZA AYALA' AND c.nombre = 'LUIS' AND c.dni = 40567564;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS Cantidad, SUM(c.importe) AS SubTotal, SUM(c.importe) * 0.18 AS IGV, SUM(c.importe) + (SUM(c.importe) * 0.18) AS ImporteTotal FROM comprobante c WHERE fecha BETWEEN '2023-05-01' AND '2023-06-03';
